AIChanges: {
	Lepus:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Diseaster bunnies move much faster
		-Small eggs hatch faster

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Small eggs cannot be destroyed
		-Small eggs hatch even faster
		-Large eggs hatch faster

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Creates 2 falling knives when fast falling
		-Creates 4 falling knives on weak jumps
		-Shoots exploding eggs while charging up
		-Occasionally stops and vomits
		-Diseaster bunnies inflict guilty on hit
		-Most attacks inflict either stunned, rotting or defenseless

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled
		-Increased falling knives to 4 on fast fall
		-Increased falling knives to 5 on weak jumps
		-Shoots explosive eggs much faster
		'''
	Turkor:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Both dash and projectile attacks have alternate variants
		-Knives travel further

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Sometimes uses both melee and ranged attacks at once
		-Knives travel even further

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Body creates a spiral of knives every now and then
		-Most attacks inflict either guilty, rotting, or stunned

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled
		-Knife spiral only happens below 75% health
		'''
	Ocram:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Increased dash displacement
		-Increased dash displacement further in phase 2
		-Cannot take damage when transitioning phases
		-Shoots skulls after phase 1 laser barrage
		-Shoots skulls during phase 2 laser barrage
		-Most attacks inflict burning blood or brain rot

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Increased dash displacement even further overall
		-Phase 1 burst lasers shoots 3 lines instead of 1
		-Shoots a lot more skulls

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Servants can shoot homing spectral flames
		-Dashes curve a bit and leave a trail of scythes
		-Has a third phase with new attacks
		-Most attacks inflict a variety of debuffs

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled
		-Increased scythes in phase 3
		-Phase 3 laser sweeps faster
		'''
	Thorn:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Splinter balls are accompanied by a barrage of splinters
		-Leeching vines spawn faster

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Splinter balls explode into more splinters
		-Leeching vines spawn even faster

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Splinter balls follow the the player for a short duration
		-Most attacks inflict infested and rotting

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled
		'''
	Erhan:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Shoots homing light during laser beam rain in phase 1
		-Spawns twice the amount of light swords in phase 1
		-Throws spears while the Bible is attacking in phase 2

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Erhan does not get tired
		-Enters later phases sooner
		-Throws spears while the Bible is attacking in phase 1

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Most attacks inflict smite

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled
		'''
	Keeper:
		'''
