		-Increased projectiles for circle and glow spiral attack
		'''
	PutridPinky:
		'''
		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Revengeance}
		-Burst laser interval reduced
		-Laser beam attack is followed up by a dual helix attack
		-Dashes a bunch of times after invisibility attack
		-Shoots a homing projectile during spinning hooks attack

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Death}
		-Attacks faster overall
		-Burst laser interval further reduced
		-Dash displacement greatly increased

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.Eternity}
		-Calamity changes are disabled
		-Phase 1 has an entire moveset which is meant to be a weaker version of phase 2
		-Shoots a giant blob that splits into 6 smaller blobs before firing a laser
		-Hovers besides the player then shoots homing blobs along with singlular helices after invisibility attack
		-Most attacks inflict lethargic

		{$Mods.RevengeancePlus.Modes.EterniDeath}
		-Calamity changes are reenabled (except for faster overall attack speed)
		-Giant blobs have slight homing and split into 8 instead of 6
		-Dash attack happens after single helix attack instead of invisibility
		-Dual helices wave out much further
		'''
	PharaohsCurse:
